{"tid":2258642,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"命運石之門十週年新作","createTime":"2020-10-26T08:04:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T05:54:27.000Z","uid":41414,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b0051094cd65b34fb96f23ba5fa7675d8a770910","tid":2258642,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:04:11.000Z","msg":"作為《命運石之門》十週年 10 項特別企劃第九項的「科學 ADV 系列全新企劃《STEINS;????（???? 之名稱尚未明朗）》」，志倉千代丸表示《命運石之門》是以 0 與 1 的故事完結，再接續做下去的話就會變成糞作，因此本作類似於在過去推出的《Chaos；HEAd》&amp;《混沌之子（Chaos;Child）》相互關聯的作品，可以將本作想成是《命運石之門》的續篇，卻又不能說是 Fan disc（粉絲向追加故事後續），而是一部完全的新系列。而志倉千代丸也證實在 CAST 方面，宮野真守、関智一以及今井麻美會出演本作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=205301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2Fdetail.php%3Fsn%3D205301&d=BeC7y%2FNJ2VFG1TiFYPS6oNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=cc2577ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=205301</a>"},{"pid":"2b2dfd4a057ef0e2707262ab05ada88f9e7346f6","tid":2258642,"uid":263534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:07:41.000Z","msg":"終於肯開新路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdfab0418957e91d70aa4c150cbb38d30320b10","tid":2258642,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:23:32.000Z","msg":"正呀喂"},{"pid":"c159267e3c7af9535c349b5802f21dc6485091d7","tid":2258642,"uid":316697,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:24:58.000Z","msg":"宮野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15fc2440db78341f3c4f44ec34a6bdb9fccb3eda","tid":2258642,"uid":316697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"關智一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd36a13c3c1e5e521fe36c9cfc6d33d6c5848f93","tid":2258642,"uid":300901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T08:28:46.000Z